{"data":[{"date":"07:44 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (17h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6): Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-hagl-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-226-khong-con-duong-lui.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh l\u1ec7nh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y?</h2><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: G\u1ed7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL t\u1eebng c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e0ng \u0111i v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u1ea5t khi ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c, &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u1edf kh\u00e2u th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0y \u1ea3i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf t\u1ed1p cu\u1ed1i TP.HCM, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 3 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua g\u1ed3m th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (17h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (17h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/HAGL-Saigon.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2 v\u00e0 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu ch\u1eaft chiu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, HAGL c\u1ea7n&nbsp; gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n trong n\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin trong thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb HAGL \u00edt khi gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1edbm. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u00e0i to\u00e1n ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua th\u00eam \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1edfi. B\u1edfi khi m\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, NHM c\u0169ng \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng CLB HAGL s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau c\u01a1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi HAGL, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u1edf m\u1ed9t th\u00e1i c\u1ef1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c.&nbsp;Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 5-2 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, l\u00fac n\u00e0y tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111ang l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd mang tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Pleiku trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi HAGL s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sai Gon vs HAGL\" title=\"S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu cho HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n v\u1edbi HAGL. 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec S\u00e0i G\u00f2n th\u1eafng 2 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua 1 trong \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p HAGL v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1. V\u00ec l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3,&nbsp;h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 sau 90 ph\u00fat so t\u00e0i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trong chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i n\u00e0y S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 n\u00e0o, trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HAGL ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi. Trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u1eb7p ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Osmar v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7&nbsp;Vincent Bossou. R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i binh, HAGL s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2, d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00ec trong tay \u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c thay th\u1ebf.&nbsp;\u0110\u00e1ng lo nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 li\u1ec7u &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; c\u00f3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 k\u00e9m \u1edf 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 8 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 2 V-League. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p S\u00e0i G\u00f2n s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL c\u1ea7n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 26 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u nay 22/6 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich thi dau vong 15 V-League 2018\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Lich-thi-dau-vong-15-V-League.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai-168-189175.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai-168-189175.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018: HAGL tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i?</span><br />\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi-168-189139.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi-168-189139.html\">Thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HAGL s\u1eafp tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi?</span><br />\r\nSau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c 3 ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 5 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL: Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n</span><br />\r\nCh\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3754","checkdouble":"189221"},{"date":"06:46 22/06","title":"\u0102n burger mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed tr\u1ecdn \u0111\u1eddi n\u1ebfu ... c\u00f3 b\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 World Cup","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/an-burger-mien-phi-tron-doi-neu-co-bau-voi-cau-thu-du-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eeda h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n nhanh Burger King t\u1ea1i Nga \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m t\u1edbi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef n\u00f3i tr\u00ean.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">V\u1eeba qua, chu\u1ed7i c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng \u0103n nhanh Burger King tung chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean VK, m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 Facebook c\u1ee7a Nga.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Burger King t\u1ea1i Nga ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m m\u00f9a World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Burger King t\u1ea1i Nga ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m m\u00f9a World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Quang-cao-Burger-King-tai-Nga-phan-cam-mua-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u1eb7ng th\u01b0\u1edfng cho ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef mang b\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup \u1edf Nga c\u1ee7a Burger King tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng VK. \u1ea2nh: Deadspin Photograph.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nN\u1ed9i dung qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Burger King kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u1eb7ng th\u01b0\u1edfng 3 tri\u1ec7u rup (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01a1n 1 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng) v\u00e0 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed tr\u1ecdn \u0111\u1eddi \u0103n burger Whoppers (l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u00e1nh \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a Burger King v\u1edbi nh\u00e2n g\u1ed3m th\u1ecbt b\u00f2 n\u01b0\u1edbng, x\u00e0 l\u00e1ch, c\u00e0 chua, h\u00e0nh t\u00e2y v\u00e0 d\u01b0a mu\u1ed1i) cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef n\u00e0o c\u00f3 b\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nNgay sau khi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, Burger King \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1eef d\u1ed9i t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn. C\u00f4ng ty n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i xo\u00e1 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng VK.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nan nhan trong vu hiep dam bi Burger King Nga loi dung hinh anh cho chien dich quang cao. Anh: RT.\" title=\"N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n trong v\u1ee5 hi\u1ebfp d\u00e2m b\u1ecb Burger King Nga l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. \u1ea2nh: RT.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/BK_russia_1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n trong v\u1ee5 hi\u1ebfp d\u00e2m b\u1ecb Burger King Nga l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. \u1ea2nh: RT.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng Burger King t\u1ea1i Nga s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c thu h\u00fat d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, h\u00e3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t n\u1eef thi\u1ebfu ni\u00ean 16 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb hi\u1ebfp d\u00e2m trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nH\u1ecd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Diana Shurygina d\u00f9ng c\u1eed ch\u1ec9 tay \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 c\u00f4 b\u00e9 \u0111\u00e3 u\u1ed1ng m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat r\u01b0\u1ee3u vodka trong b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh minh ho\u1ea1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh khuy\u1ebfn m\u00e3i mua 1 t\u1eb7ng 1.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n h\u01a1n, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf Nga m\u00e0 tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Burger King mang ti\u1ebfng x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch marketing x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m t\u1edbi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef v\u00e0 tr\u1ebb em g\u00e1i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Burger King Singapore loi dung hinh anh phu nu dang ha mieng va chu Blow - co nghia la thoi va de bi hieu nham mang tinh goi duc trong khau hieu quang cao san pham moi. Anh: Adweek.\" title=\"Burger King Singapore l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef \u0111ang h\u00e1 mi\u1ec7ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eef Blow - c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 th\u1ed5i v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u nh\u1ea7m mang t\u00ednh g\u1ee3i d\u1ee5c trong kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1edbi. \u1ea2nh: Adweek.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/bk_blow_ad_1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Burger King Singapore l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef \u0111ang h\u00e1 mi\u1ec7ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eef Blow - c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 th\u1ed5i v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u nh\u1ea7m mang t\u00ednh g\u1ee3i d\u1ee5c trong kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1edbi. \u1ea2nh: Adweek.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nN\u0103m 2009, t\u1ea1i Singapore, c\u00f4ng ty n\u00e0y t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u00e1nh burger d\u00e0i 7 inch (17 cm) v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh g\u1ee3i d\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef \u0111ang h\u00e1 mi\u1ec7ng v\u00e0 c\u00e2u kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u \u201cN\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y ng\u1ea5t ng\u00e2y\u201d.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu n\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee5p trong \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u00e0y th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 bi\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3753","checkdouble":"189214"},{"date":"22:26 21/06","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Emre Can gia nh\u1eadp Juventus d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng CNTD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/21/chinh-thuc-emre-can-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u00cdt ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u00f4ng tin ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can gia nh\u1eadp Juventus ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp CLB Italia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.\r\n</h2><h2>Emre Can ra m\u1eaft Juventus<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 do t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus. Th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ed1t t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 5, v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 sau khi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00f4m nay (21/6), B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Emre Can. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus, v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y (b\u1edfi anh kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1n ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Emre Can gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Emre Can gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/chinh-thuc-emre-can-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Emre Can gia nh\u1eadp Juventus b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t d\u00f2ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean trang web, Juventus cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cEmre Can l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 linh ho\u1ea1t, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t, s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m t\u1eeb Liverpool. Anh c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 150 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf, ghi 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Leverkusen v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cJuve s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh ra t\u1ea1i Frankfurt, sau khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi Bayern Munich. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1i Juventus \u0111\u1ec1u vui m\u1eebng ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Emre Can \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y!\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c r\u1eddi Juve. Stefano Sturaro \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham, trong khi Barca \u0111ang theo s\u00e1t Miralem Pjanic. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Emre Can gia nh\u1eadp Juventus l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 2 trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, sau Mattia Perin chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Genoa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-juventus-voi-gia-45-trieu-bang-172-189169.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/9/arsenal-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-juventus-voi-gia-45-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-juventus-voi-gia-45-trieu-bang-172-189169.html\">Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n sao kh\u1ee7ng cho Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nJuventus mu\u1ed1n mua Hector Bellerin c\u1ee7a Arsenal, song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-ra-gia-pjanic-it-nhat-80-trieu-euro-176-189062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/7/13/miralem-pjanic-juventus-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-ra-gia-pjanic-it-nhat-80-trieu-euro-176-189062.html\">Juventus b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t cho Real v\u00e0 Barca</span><br>\r\nJuventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 khi m\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m Real...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3752","checkdouble":"189191"},{"date":"18:25 21/06","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018: HAGL tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/14/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018.\r\n\r\n</h2><br />\r\n<h2>HAGL quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB HAGL ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u2018kh\u00f4ng may\u2019 \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Tr\u1eadn thua 1-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o \u2018g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh\u2019 d\u1ed9i v\u00e0o tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u201cG\u1ed7\u201d tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 c\u0169 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f3t vay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, HAGL \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 phong \u0111\u1ed9. H\u1ecd m\u1ea5t nguy\u00ean c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh, T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2. V\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, \u201cG\u1ed7\u201d c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f9ng 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 TP.HCM khi\u1ebfn HAGL \u0111ang xa d\u1ea7n nh\u00f3m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 9 v\u1edbi 17 \u0111i\u1ec3m, k\u00e9m t\u1ed1p 3 c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng t\u1edbi 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00ec v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 HAGL c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 3 khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018 HAGL tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018 HAGL tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/ket-qua-sai-gon-vs-hagl-tran-dau-vong-5-vleague-2018.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB HAGL li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay t\u1eeb S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi \u201cG\u1ed7\u201d, c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi gia t\u0103ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i V-League. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p HAGL, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mang tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Pleiku, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft th\u00fac t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB\u00a0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00edt ch\u1ecbu s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u00e2m l\u00fd nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y song x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng HAGL nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC nh\u1edd d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, phong \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua vi\u1ec7c th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 1, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1edfi b\u1ecf \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m s\u01a1 \u0111\u1eb3ng, HAGL \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u01a1i l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1ch th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1ch th\u1eafng?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u2018ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em\u2019 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, xem ra 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi t\u1ea7m tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. M\u1eb7c kh\u00e1c, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam cho vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tai n\u1ea1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \"c\u1eeda tr\u00ean\" b\u1edfi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh qua th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. L\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda nh\u1eefng Quang H\u1ea3i, Duy M\u1ea1nh b\u1edfi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 23/6,\u00a0H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, trong khi SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i\u00a0tr\u1ea3 c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL khi l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00f9ng m\u1eb7t sau pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Kim Jin-seo. M\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, xem ch\u1eebng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ha Noi thua dam Sai Gon o vong 14 V-League 2018.\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB\u00a0H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu l\u00e0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i gia t\u0103ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111ang h\u01a1n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch an to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, v\u00f2ng 15 V-League c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Ngh\u1ec7 An vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa TP.HCM vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i TP.HCM vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111ang chia s\u1ebb hai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean BXH. N\u1ebfu Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng th\u00e0nh 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 15 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 23 v\u00e0 24/6. Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich thi dau vong 15 V-League 2018\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Lich-thi-dau-vong-15-V-League.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL: Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n</span><br />\r\nCh\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi-168-189139.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi-168-189139.html\">Thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HAGL s\u1eafp tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi?</span><br />\r\nSau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c 3 ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 5 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/clb-hagl-noi-gi-sau-khi-tang-tien-lai-ngua-quen-duong-cu-168-189067.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/6/clb-hagl-noi-gi-sau-khi-tang-tien-lai-ngua-quen-duong-cu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/clb-hagl-noi-gi-sau-khi-tang-tien-lai-ngua-quen-duong-cu-168-189067.html\">CLB HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn l\u1ea1i ng\u1ef1a quen \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169?</span><br />\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh xung quanh vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn d\u00ednh \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t l\u1ea7n hai v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018-325-188738.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018-325-188738.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL (V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018)</span><br />\r\nD\u00f9 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo san b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00f2n H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3751","checkdouble":"189175"},{"date":"22:50 21/06","title":"N\u00d3NG: M.U ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Fred","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/chinh-thuc-mu-cong-bo-tan-binh-fred.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n sau World Cup, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y M.U c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Fred b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n clip c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2><div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/21/fred.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\">\r\n<h2><br />\r\nM.U ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Fred<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/21/fred.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi CLB Shakhtar Donetsk v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 6, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00f4m nay, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Fred.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/21/fred.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o Anh b\u00e1o tin \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t bom t\u1ea5n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, v\u00e0 2 b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 tranh th\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu gi\u1eefa Selecao v\u1edbi \u0110T Croatia t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 Anfield, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 xin ph\u00e9p HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi Carrington \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/21/fred.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00f4m nay (21/6), anh m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Man United &ndash; khi Fred \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n clip c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, M.U \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng linh v\u1eadt l\u00e0 ch\u00fa Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf &ldquo;Fred the Red&rdquo; (tr\u00f9ng t\u00ean v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil) ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u00e0n piano, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 bom t\u1ea5n Alexis Sanchez m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C MU c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Fred h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C MU c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Fred h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/chinh-thuc-mu-cong-bo-tan-binh-fred.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Fred</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br />\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn nay Fred m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, sau h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Diogo Dalot t\u1eeb FC Porto.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/21/fred.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Fred \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Casemiro, trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Selecao. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn anh ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup, nh\u01b0ng HLV Tite cho bi\u1ebft ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 anh s\u1ebd s\u1edbm c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/21/fred.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Fred s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Man United \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn sau 2 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Mourinho s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111em v\u1ec1 Old Trafford m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7, c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/21/fred.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i \u0111o\u1ea1n clip M.U c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Fred</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/21/fred.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tat-tan-tat-ve-fred-bom-tan-dau-tien-cua-mu-mua-he-nay-172-187872.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/tat-tan-tat-ve-fred-bom-tan-dau-tien-cua-mu-mua-he-nay.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tat-tan-tat-ve-fred-bom-tan-dau-tien-cua-mu-mua-he-nay-172-187872.html\">T\u1ea5t t\u1ea7n t\u1eadt v\u1ec1 Fred - bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a MU m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span><br />\r\nT\u1ed1i qua (5/6) theo gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Man United \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin Fred gia nh\u1eadp MU m\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-dieu-xay-ra-khi-fred-cap-ben-man-united-172-187821.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/chiem-nguong-tai-nang-cua-tan-binh-mu-tien-ve-fred.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-dieu-xay-ra-khi-fred-cap-ben-man-united-172-187821.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra khi Fred c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Man United</span><br />\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred gia nh\u1eadp MU ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng gi\u1edd, khi anh \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u1ea3n doanh Carrington.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/co-nguoi-yeu-xinh-dep-cua-tan-binh-mu-188-187876.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/co-nguoi-yeu-xinh-dep-cua-tan-binh-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/co-nguoi-yeu-xinh-dep-cua-tan-binh-mu-188-187876.html\">C\u00f4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau xinh \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh M.U</span><br />\r\nSau khi M.U x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred t\u1eeb Shakhtar Donetsk, \u0111\u1ed9i WAGs CLB n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng y\u00eau v\u00e0 hi\u1ec1n l\u00e0nh Monique Salum.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3750","checkdouble":"189182"},{"date":"22:03 21/06","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man United, bom t\u1ea5n Fred n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/21/chuyen-toi-man-united-bom-tan-fred-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u00cdt ph\u00fat v\u1eeba qua, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Fred ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a anh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2><strong>Fred h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i t\u1eeb khi c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Shakhtar Donetsk, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Fred. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Old Trafford v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Nga \u0111\u1ec3 chinh chi\u1ebfn World Cup c\u00f9ng \u0110T Brazil, v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111o\u1ea1n clip n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 6. Ch\u1ec9 khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea5y ph\u00e9p lao \u0111\u1ed9ng, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh, v\u00e0 M.U c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 bom t\u1ea5n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Fred cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i, th\u1eadt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m vinh d\u1ef1 l\u1edbn khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cho Man United.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Manchester United &ndash; nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn. Khi t\u00f4i c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng nghe trong tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, Manchester United ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fred ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U\" title=\"Fred ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/chuyen-toi-man-united-bom-tan-fred-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fred ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1i t\u00ean Nh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t SV\u0110 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi Ryan Giggs trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 may tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh anh \u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u00e0 anh \u1ea5y t\u1eebng mang.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Premier League r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. T\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u1edf Premier League, v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng M.U gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1. T\u00f4i n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi, v\u00e0 xin g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi CLB Shakhtar Donetsk, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 trong 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y, s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 World Cup c\u00f9ng \u0110T Brazil&rdquo; &ndash; Fred ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ra m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i \u0111o\u1ea1n clip M.U c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Fred</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/21/fred.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-mu-cong-bo-tan-binh-fred-172-189182.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/chinh-thuc-mu-cong-bo-tan-binh-fred.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-mu-cong-bo-tan-binh-fred-172-189182.html\">N\u00d3NG: M.U ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Fred</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n sau World Cup, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y M.U c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Fred b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n clip c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-dieu-xay-ra-khi-fred-cap-ben-man-united-172-187821.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/chiem-nguong-tai-nang-cua-tan-binh-mu-tien-ve-fred.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-dieu-xay-ra-khi-fred-cap-ben-man-united-172-187821.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra khi Fred c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Man United</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred gia nh\u1eadp MU ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng gi\u1edd, khi anh \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u1ea3n doanh Carrington.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tat-tan-tat-ve-fred-bom-tan-dau-tien-cua-mu-mua-he-nay-172-187872.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/tat-tan-tat-ve-fred-bom-tan-dau-tien-cua-mu-mua-he-nay.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tat-tan-tat-ve-fred-bom-tan-dau-tien-cua-mu-mua-he-nay-172-187872.html\">T\u1ea5t t\u1ea7n t\u1eadt v\u1ec1 Fred - bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a MU m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i qua (5/6) theo gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Man United \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin Fred gia nh\u1eadp MU m\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3749","checkdouble":"189186"},{"date":"14:50 21/06","title":"M\u1eb9 Messi: \"Con trai t\u00f4i kh\u00f3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG Argentina\"","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/21/me-messi-con-trai-toi-khoc-nhieu-lan-trong-mau-ao-dtqg-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e0 Celia Cuccittini chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m bu\u1ed3n m\u00e0 con trai Lionel Messi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Messi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn khi \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn Argentina h\u00f2a Iceland h\u00f4m 16/6. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u1ed1t tr\u1ea7m m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 M10 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n, sau ba l\u1ea7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec t\u1ea1i World Cup 2014, Copa America 2015 v\u00e0 2016.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u1eb9 Messi Con trai t\u00f4i kh\u00f3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"M\u1eb9 Messi Con trai t\u00f4i kh\u00f3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/mes2-2879-1529552716.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi r\u01a1i l\u1ec7 sau khi s\u00fat h\u1ecfng lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u khi\u1ebfn Argentina thua trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Copa America 2016.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb9 Messi chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh El Trece h\u00f4m 20/6: ''M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Messi l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh World Cup. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ham mu\u1ed1n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. Gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y n\u00f3 \u0111au kh\u1ed5 v\u00e0 kh\u00f3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n. H\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai, n\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup n\u0103m nay''.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng, Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Argentina. N\u0103m 2016, anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n sau khi s\u00fat h\u1ecfng lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Copa America.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n''Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111au kh\u1ed5 v\u00ec nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u00e0nh cho Messi. Khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta n\u00f3i Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m khi ch\u01a1i cho Argentina, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eb9. Gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t y\u00eau n\u00f3 v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac'', b\u00e0 Celia cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMessi t\u1eebng tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n s\u1ee9c \u00e9p khi l\u1eadp hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Ecuador trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup (3-1). \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Argentina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0 xem gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu h\u00f2a ho\u1eb7c thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n''T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y Messi \u0111\u00e3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u01a1n, b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u01b0\u1edbc n\u00f3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn. T\u00f4i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi n\u00f3 h\u00e3y t\u1ef1 vui v\u1ebb, s\u1ed1ng cho hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. C\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh lu\u00f4n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 n\u00f3'', b\u00e0 Celia chia s\u1ebb.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3748","checkdouble":"189155"},{"date":"15:15 21/06","title":"VPF l\u1ea1i thu\u00ea tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ngo\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i V-League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/11/22/vpf-lai-thue-trong-tai-ngoai-lam-viec-tai-vleague.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u VPF \u00f4ng Tr\u1ea7n Anh T\u00fa \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd m\u1eddi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ngo\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"VPF thu\u00ea tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ngo\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i V-League  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"VPF thu\u00ea tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ngo\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i V-League  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/22/vpf-lai-thue-trong-tai-ngoai-lam-viec-tai-vleague.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>VPF thu\u00ea tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ngo\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League n\u0103m nay, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 song c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i V-League v\u1eabn l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n b\u1ecb treo c\u00f2i v\u00f4 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o VPF \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eddi c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u quan tr\u1ecdng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng Tr\u1ea7n Anh T\u00fa, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VPF kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t gi\u1eefa m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018 trong ba ng\u00e0y t\u1eeb 18/06 \u0111\u1ebfn 20/06.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, do v\u1eady, Ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u00fang k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n m\u1eddi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i FIFA ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i khi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t \u0111ua tranh quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u0103ng cao s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e2n c\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \"nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m\", Ban \u0110i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh VPF c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi VFF v\u00e0 C\u1ee5c C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t h\u00ecnh s\u1ef1 (B\u1ed9 C\u00f4ng an) \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba, b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m s\u1ef1 trong s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 minh b\u1ea1ch cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3747","checkdouble":"189156"},{"date":"15:31 21/06","title":"Inter Milan h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n sao Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/13/inter-milan-hoi-muon-sao-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Davide Zappacosta c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ef1u sao Torino 1 n\u0103m k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Davide Zappacosta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Davide Zappacosta t\u1eeb Torino, song m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. Anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 12 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Davide Zappacosta h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Davide Zappacosta h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/13/inter-milan-hoi-muon-sao-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zappacosta ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Davide Zappacosta l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, song anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n khi\u1ebfn BL\u0110 Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ef1u sao Torino ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Davide Zappacosta song kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter Milan h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Zappacosta</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Davide Zappacosta c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ef1u sao Torino 1 n\u0103m k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zappacosta cua Chelsea\" title=\"Zappacosta cua Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/13/Hau-ve-Davide-Zappacosta-noi-ve-su-khac-nghiet-o-EPL-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Inter h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Zappacosta</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh Milan kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t Zappacosta ngay \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. N\u1ebfu ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, Inter s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Inter Milan. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, h\u1ecd \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Zappacosta c\u0169ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu Conte \u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Stamford Bridge, Zappacosta s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3746","checkdouble":"189154"},{"date":"15:47 21/06","title":"S\u1ed1c: Roy Keane t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n... \"v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u\" tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Ferguson","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/soc-roy-keane-tung-muon-vat-dau-tro-ly-hlv-ferguson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo m\u1ed9t ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u2013 Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRoy Keane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Roy Keane t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. Sau khi r\u1eddi M.U, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169, b\u1edfi anh t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Sir Alex &ndash; HLV Carlos Queiroz c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7. \u00d4ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Ferguson v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2002/03, gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i quay l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2004. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Queiroz \u0111ang l\u00e0 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Iran chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, v\u00e0 Keane \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed9c &ldquo;\u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9&rdquo; n\u0103m x\u01b0a.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc&rdquo; &ndash; Keane cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Man United. Carlos Queiroz c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u1edfi m\u1edf cho l\u1eafm, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi nghe s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz khi c\u00f2n \u1edf M.U\" title=\"Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/soc-roy-keane-tung-muon-vat-dau-tro-ly-hlv-ferguson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz khi c\u00f2n \u1edf M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean khi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ra \u0111i, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2004, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Queiroz th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tranh c\u00e3i n\u1ea3y l\u1eeda. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y nghi ng\u1edd l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u l\u1ea1i qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u00f4ng \u1ea5y r\u1eddi b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111e d\u1ecda v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. Carlos Queiroz l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong vai tr\u00f2 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a HLV Ferguson, nh\u01b0ng Carlos Queiroz kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Patrice Evra t\u1eebng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 g\u1ea7n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi b\u1ecb Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz, HLV n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2008, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n b\u1ecb tr\u00ed HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. \u0110\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2011, \u00f4ng nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Iran cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-khung-tuyen-duc-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189082.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/5/26/mu-nham-sao-khung-tuyen-duc-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-khung-tuyen-duc-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189082.html\">MU nh\u1eafm sao kh\u1ee7ng tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n mua trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea-172-189132.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea-172-189132.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o t\u1edbi CLB Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh Ruben Loftus-Cheek m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o CLB Chelsea v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3745","checkdouble":"189159"},{"date":"16:21 21/06","title":"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i MU v\u00e0 Tottenham v\u1ee5 sao Aston Villa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/liverpool-muon-danh-bai-mu-va-tottenham-vu-sao-aston-villa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jack Grealish</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Jack Grealish l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng, ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ho\u1eb7c trung phong c\u1eafm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/Liverpool-muon-mua-Jack-Grealish-cua-Aston-Villa-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jack Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 ghi 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap Aston Villa l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng, song \u0111\u1ec3 thua Fulham.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. MU quan t\u00e2m Jack Grealish, Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Pochettino c\u1ee7a Tottenham c\u0169ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Jack Grealish \u1edf Spurs.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, HLV Klopp \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a n\u0103ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/liverpool-muon-danh-bai-mu-va-tottenham-vu-sao-aston-villa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Tottenham v\u00e0 MU trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, Liverpool ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp r\u1ea5t m\u00e1t tay v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Jack Grealish ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc \u1edf s\u00e2n Anfield.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAston Villa \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 v\u00f4 danh nh\u01b0 Jack Grealish.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang b\u1ecb dao \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p BL\u0110 Aston Villa \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish, 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Aston Villa nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3744","checkdouble":"189164"},{"date":"16:54 21/06","title":"Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n sao kh\u1ee7ng cho Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/9/arsenal-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-juventus-voi-gia-45-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Hector Bellerin c\u1ee7a Arsenal, song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus h\u1ecfi mua Bellerin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Hector Bellerin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Arsenal. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Hector Bellerin v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Hector Bellerin v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/9/arsenal-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-juventus-voi-gia-45-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Bellerin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Theo The Sun, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Hector Bellerin, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Bellerin, h\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Arsenal nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Juventus c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Italia s\u1ebd c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi Anh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ngay \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Bellerin</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/juventus-mua-hau-ve-hector-bellerin-176-172922.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Bellerin </span>c\u1ee7a Arsenal, song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bellerin\" title=\"Bellerin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/4/Hector-Bellerin-phat-bieu-ve-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Bellerin v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, HLV Unai Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bellerin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i\u00a0sao 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDanh s\u00e1ch 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Alexandre Lacazette, Granit Xhaka, Pierre Emerick Aubameyang, Henrikh Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh Hector Bellerin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMU v\u00e0 Barca c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, song Arsenal s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3743","checkdouble":"189169"},{"date":"17:18 21/06","title":"\"MU c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2016/9/22/mk-dons-tha-thiet-moi-chao-ryan-giggs.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ryan Giggs ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, M.U tr\u1eafng tay khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ryan Giggs ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ryan Giggs ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Ryan-Giggs-phat-bieu-ve-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u00e2n binh, bao g\u1ed3m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dalot. 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Giggs khuy\u00ean MU mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ryan Giggs ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"cuu tien ve Ryan Giggs\" title=\"cuu tien ve Ryan Giggs\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/22/Giggs-muon-tien-ve-Aaron-Ramsey-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ryan Giggs mu\u1ed1n MU mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Mourinho n\u00ean mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 Rio Ferdinand trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t bi\u1ebft ch\u1ec9 huy h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, M.U s\u1ebd h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n thua\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cM.U c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. Carrick \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, M.U thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ryan-giggs-khuyen-mourinho-ky-hop-dong-voi-sao-real-madrid-172-189040.html\" target=\"_blank\">Giggs c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n MU mua Gareth Bale</span> c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, \u00f4ng tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Man \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGiggs c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o Mourinho, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n gi\u1ecfi. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a M.U s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c M.U s\u1ebd c\u00f3 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3742","checkdouble":"189170"}]}